{"type": "article", "id": 2249, "title": "Craft Collection 厨具", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-08T17:28:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222307Io7gHF6nr3cRVL01.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Simon Legald 近日为丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 设计了一系列由大理石与橡木制作而成的厨房用具 Craft Collection 。这套厨具大胆巧妙地将两种不同的材质融合，大理石的纹路点缀着橡木朴实粗糙的外观，不但没有失去厨房用具的实用性，更创造出一种另类的新潮风格。定价 95－175 美元不等，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/designers/simon-legald\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222305P5vOXKEo1zey8Z4G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222306boEfQMAD6duxI02O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060522230615AlXZ3hTLmtGeVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}